How do you use the key gen?

Manual: Use R'n'R_KeyGen.exe (TRiViUM folder on DVD). Instruction in Pictures: 4Dummies.png (TRiViUM folder on DVD) 1. Run the R'n'R_KeyGen.exe and press the Get Num 2. Copy the resulting number in the window of activation StarForce 3. Click I already have an activation key 4. Copy your Hardware ID in the keygen 5. Click Get Key in keygen 6. Copy the resulting key in the box and click Next StarForce 7. Play!
